---
Long-term verifiability attestation and offline verification

Usage: franken-node ltv <COMMAND>

Commands:
  attest        Produce self-contained long-term verification evidence from a signature-verified incident bundle
  verify-as-of  Verify long-term evidence as of a claimed time through the offline verifier SDK
  help          Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
